OL,6,FMark said: "Jurgen comes down and
OL,7,Fgreats me with that smile, a proper
OL,8,Fman hug and that laugh that we have
OL,9,Fall grown to love over the last nine
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,F"To say he is the normal one is an
OL,13,Funderstatement. To sit and share
OL,14,Ffootball stories and talk about
OL,15,FMissedABeat was something that I will
OL,16,Fnever forget. It will live with me
OL,17,Fforever."
